<head>PEARL</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">珠</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>SMALL SHINING BALL which GROWS IN MUSSELS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for a rounded pearl is zhū 珠.</p>
<p>2. Jī 璣 refers to a smaller variety of a non-round pearl.</p>
        </div>
